summary: A small world space containing a large nordic structure
descriptionHtml:
A player home world space countaining:

Smithing area complete with forge, smelter, tanning rack, grinding wheel, and armor work bench
Wood chopping area
Mill
(Reasonably) Harmless elder dragon
Player home with huge amount of chests, weapon racks, weapon displace cases, and weapon wall mounts
Alchemy Table with Apothecary\'s Satchel for storage
Enchanting table
Dwemer elevator to a dwemer oculory
college of winterhold building with a huge garden


The entrance is in Whiterun behind War Maiden\'s

Mannequins and book shelves are currently not working
Ore mining will be implemented soon
author: jahnarae
